title: Oceanic Pro League Round 1 tipping! Who are you backing?
body:
Hey everyone! 

http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/sites/default/files/styles/scale_xlarge/public/upload/opl_split_1_announce.jpg?itok=aX-Y1qp7

Day one of the [Oceanic Pro League](http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/esports/esports-editorial/pro-league-coming-oceania) is fast approaching!
I want to see who you think will win, check out the links below and put in your vote!
All tipping closes 1 hour before matches start so make sure to get your vote in on time.

Anyone that can pick **ALL** 8 games correct will get a **10 win IP Boost!**

**Thursday Feb 5th Games**
[Thursday tipping form](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1LX35ZYqLWJBPEXFmLRIwWmpz0DpvP0WsJMKYNNWdJTo/viewform)

6pm AEDT Chiefs vs Legacy
7pm approx. 4Not vs Legacy
8pm approx. Chiefs vs Sudden Fear
9pm approx. Sudden Fear vs 4Not 


**Monday Feb 9th Games**
[Monday Tipping form](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/19SwS6bVa_Ag9RgMTXOW9MpSn66xuAHMF8OEd0cgGCnQ/viewform)

6pm AEDT	Avant Garde vs Dire Wolves
7pm approx.	Rich Gang vs Avant Garde
8pm approx.	Dire Wolves vs Team Immunity
9pm approx.	Team Immunity vs Rich Gang


You can catch all the action at our [twitch channel](http://www.twitch.tv/riotgamesoceania)

Comment below with what you picked and why!
